"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The president says that fighting has stopped because of the ceasefire, and he believes he does not need approval from Congress.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ceasefire Stops Fighting\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente dice que la pelea ha parado por el alto al fuego, y cree que no necesita permiso del Congreso.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Alto al fuego para pelea\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A shortage of fertilizer due to the conflict with Iran might lower crop yields and increase prices, according to the head of Yara.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fertilizer Shortage Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una falta de fertilizante por el conflicto con Ir\u00e1n podr\u00eda bajar la cantidad de cultivos y subir los precios, seg\u00fan el jefe de Yara.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Falta de fertilizante\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A French nun was attacked in an unprovoked incident, as harassment of Christians by Jewish extremists in the city increases.\",            \"english_title\": \"Nun Attacked in City\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una monja francesa fue atacada sin raz\u00f3n, mientras el acoso a cristianos por extremistas jud\u00edos en la ciudad aumenta.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque a monja\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Mladic, who is 84 years old, was sentenced to life in prison for genocide, war crimes, and crimes against humanity during the Bosnian war from 1992 to 1995.\",            \"english_title\": \"Mladic Sentenced to Life\",            \"translated_version\": \"Mladic, que tiene 84 a\u00f1os, fue sentenciado a cadena perpetua por genocidio, cr\u00edmenes de guerra y cr\u00edmenes contra la humanidad durante la guerra de Bosnia de 1992 a 1995.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mladic a cadena perpetua\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Lindsay and Craig Foreman are facing a 10-year prison sentence after being arrested in Iran during a motorcycle tour last year.\",            \"english_title\": \"Foremans Face Prison\",            \"translated_version\": \"Lindsay y Craig Foreman enfrentan 10 a\u00f1os de prisi\u00f3n despu\u00e9s de ser arrestados en Ir\u00e1n durante un tour en moto el a\u00f1o pasado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Foreman enfrentan prisi\u00f3n\"        }    ]}"